tip_battle.message: Evrae is one mean customer that doesn't have any weaknesses, kupo. In fact, it's resistant to fire, ice, lightning and water attacks! Use Armor Break to soften it up for physical attacks, and dig in for a long battle!

sp_scores.title: Exploit Seymour Natus's weakness to holy attacks.

tip_battle.message: When Mortibody gets low on HP, it drains HP from Seymour, so it can't be defeated, kupo! But if you take out Seymour first, problem solved! Hit Seymour with holy damage, then defend yourself against his magic attacks with abilities like Magic Break and Shell, or even use the summon Carbuncle to cast Reflect on the whole party!
tip_battle.title: Seymour Natus & Mortibody

tip_battle.message: YKT-63 is vulnerable to fire and water! Attack with Fire Strike, Watera...any abilities that deal fire or water damage, kupo!
